payload.description: LikeEvery member of society who wants to establish a balance between their personal and professional life , women who have jobs want to make sure their homes are not neglected while they're outside developing their careers. Stay in housewives also have been trying for so long to serve their role in society by being more than just good wives and mothers from their houses .  Based on these needs we had the idea of creating an app that serves both parties   by prividing the housewives with a platform in which they can display their services and products With details like prices and informations about their  provider   to their clients that would mostly be women in outside positions.
